\c 82 
\m \bd Faarfannaa \bd*\bd 82\bd*
\s2 \bdit \zbr\bdit*Waaqayyo Abbaa Firdii Isa Hundumaa Gararraa Ta'uu Isaa (Faarfannaa Asaaf)
\m \bd 1\bd* Waaqayyo walga'ii waaqaa keessa in dhaabata, waaqayyolii gidduuttis inni firdii in dabarsa.
\m \bd 2\bd* Inni, "Isin hamma yoomiitti jal'inaan faraddu? Hamma yoomiittis warra jal'ootaaf loogdu?
\m \bd 3\bd* Warra dadhaboo fi warra abbaan irra hin jirreef dhugaa baasaaf, warra gadadamoo fi warra homaa hin qabne qajeeltootti ilaalaa!
\m \bd 4\bd* Warra dadhaboo fi warra waan barbaachisaa dhaban furaa, harka warra jal'ootaa keessaas isaan oolchaa!" in jedha.
\m \bd 5\bd* Isaan beekumsa yookiis hubannaa hin qaban, dukkana keessa in deddeebi'u; hundeen lafaa hundinuu raafamaa dha!
\m \bd 6\bd* Ani illee, "'Isin waaqayyolii dha, isin hundumti keessan ilmaan isa hundumaa gararraa jiruu ti' jedhee dubbadheera.
\m \bd 7\bd* Haa ta'u iyyuu malee, isin akka namootaa in duutu, warra gurguddoota keessaa akkuma isa tokkoos in kuftu" jedhe.
\m \bd 8\bd* Saba hundumaa kan kee waan godhatteef, ka'i yaa Waaqayyo, biyya lafaaf firdii kenni!
